## 5. The 4 Key Differences Between Sites

### 5a. Blog URL Structure

| Site | Blog post URL | Blog post page file | Related post links |
|------|--------------|--------------------|--------------------|
| Property | `/blog/{category}/{slug}` | `src/app/blog/[category]/[slug]/page.tsx` | `/blog/${categorySlug}/${slug}` |
| Dentists | `/blog/{category}/{slug}` | `src/app/blog/[category]/[slug]/page.tsx` | `/blog/${categorySlug}/${slug}` |
| **Medical** | **`/blog/{slug}` (flat)** | **`src/app/blog/[slug]/page.tsx`** | **`/blog/${slug}`** |
| Solicitors | `/blog/{category}/{slug}` | `src/app/blog/[category]/[slug]/page.tsx` | `/blog/${categorySlug}/${slug}` |

Medical is the only site with flat blog URLs. Category hub pages still exist at `/blog/{category-slug}/` on all 4 sites.

### 5b. slugifyCategory Logic

| Site | `&` handling | Example |
|------|-------------|---------|
| Property | `&` → `and` | "Section 24 & Tax Relief" → `section-24-and-tax-relief` |
| Dentists | `&` → `and` | "VAT & compliance" → `vat-and-compliance` |
| **Solicitors** | **`&` stripped** | "SRA Compliance & Trust Accounting" → `sra-compliance-trust-accounting` |
| Medical | `&` → `and` | "Incorporation & Company Structures" → `incorporation-and-company-structures` |

### 5c. CSS Theming

| Site | Approach | Primary color | Example |
|------|----------|--------------|---------|
| Property | Mix of direct Tailwind + CSS vars | emerald (`#059669`) | `text-emerald-600`, `bg-slate-50` in BlogPostRenderer |
| Dentists | CSS variables throughout | Via `var(--primary)` | `text-[var(--primary)]`, `bg-[var(--surface)]` |
| Medical | CSS variables + unique vars | teal + coral | `border-[var(--medical-teal)]`, `text-[var(--coral)]` |
| Solicitors | CSS variables throughout | Via `var(--primary)` | `text-[var(--primary)]`, `bg-[var(--surface)]` |

All sites define in `globals.css`: `--surface`, `--ink`, `--ink-soft`, `--muted`, `--border`, `--primary`, `--primary-hover`, `--accent`

### 5d. Middleware Redirects

| Site | `middleware.ts` role |
|------|---------------------|
| Property | 301 redirects: flat `/blog/{slug}` → `/blog/{category}/{slug}`; `/blog/category/{x}` → `/blog/{x}` |
| Dentists | Same flat→nested blog redirects + duplicate handling |
| Medical | Duplicate slug redirects only (no flat→nested needed — URLs are already flat) |
| Solicitors | Flat→nested redirects + `GUIDE_TO_CATEGORY_MAP` for legacy URLs |

