## 8. Blog Content Format

Blog posts are `.md` files in `{Site}/web/content/blog/` with **YAML front matter + HTML body** (not markdown syntax).

### Front Matter

```yaml
title: "Post Title"
slug: "post-slug"
canonical: "https://domain/blog/[category-slug/]slug"
metaTitle: "SEO Title | Brand"         # MUST be under 60 chars
metaDescription: "Description"         # MUST be under 155 chars
category: "Category Name"
date: "2026-04-01"
author: "Brand Editorial Team"
image: ""
altText: "Alt text for images"
h1: "Page Heading"
summary: "Brief summary"
schema: ""                             # Optional custom JSON-LD (overrides auto-generated)
faqs:
  - question: "..."
    answer: "..."
```

### HTML Body Example

```html
<p>Introductory paragraph with <strong>bold keywords</strong> and <a href="/services">internal links</a>.</p>
<h2>Section Heading</h2>
<p>Content...</p>
<h3>Subsection</h3>
<ul><li>List item</li></ul>
```

