## 10. LeadForm

- Client component at `src/components/forms/LeadForm.tsx`
- Fields: role dropdown (options from `niche.lead_form`), full name, email, phone, optional message
- Validates: email regex, UK phone format, minimum digit count
- **Submits to Supabase** `POST /rest/v1/leads` via `supabase-client.ts` using `NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_URL` + `NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY`
- Payload includes `source: niche.content_strategy.source_identifier`, `source_url` (current page URL), `submitted_at`
- On success: fires `gtag('event', 'generate_lead')`, optionally redirects to `/thank-you`

