## 17. CI Quality Gates

**`scripts/validate_blog_content.py`** checks all 236 posts for:
- Front matter completeness (title, slug, date, author, category, metaTitle, metaDescription, h1, summary)
- metaTitle ≤ 60 chars, metaDescription ≤ 155 chars
- Canonical URL present and domain-correct
- No markdown links in HTML body
- FAQ presence
- Stale year references in meta fields
- Author name matches convention
- Internal link targets exist

**GitHub Actions `content-quality-check.yml`** runs on every push/PR that touches `**/web/content/blog/**`.

